_:N376c31ff25ff431c90ed338e8d12e69c <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Mary Creagh was appointed Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State at the Department for Environment, Food and Rural Affairs on 18 July 2024. She was elected as the MP for Coventry East in July 2024.</p>\n" .
